Changes
-------

1.0.1 (2021-12-22)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Added ru translation.
* Renamed city_name field to municipality, local field to local_code.

1.0.0 (2021-12-21)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Added Django 3+ support.
* Dropped Python 2.7 support.
* Dropped Django 1.10 / 1.11 support.


